---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | AI Marketing Tools Directory">
	<section class="about">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>About AI Marketing Tools Directory</h1>
			<div class="hero-glow"></div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="content">
			<p>
				Welcome to the AI Marketing Tools Directory, your comprehensive resource for discovering 
				the best AI-powered tools to enhance your marketing strategies and workflows.
			</p>
			
			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>
				Our mission is to help marketers, businesses, and agencies navigate the rapidly evolving 
				landscape of AI marketing tools. We curate and categorize the most effective AI solutions 
				to help you find the perfect tools for your specific marketing needs.
			</p>
			
			<h2>What We Cover</h2>
			<p>
				Our directory includes AI tools across various marketing categories:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Content Creation:</strong> AI copywriting and content generation tools</li>
				<li><strong>SEO & Content Strategy:</strong> AI-powered SEO optimization and content planning</li>
				<li><strong>Social Media:</strong> AI tools for social media management and content creation</li>
				<li><strong>Email Marketing:</strong> AI solutions for email optimization and personalization</li>
				<li><strong>Visual Content:</strong> AI image and video generation tools</li>
				<li><strong>Conversational Marketing:</strong> AI chatbots and conversation optimization</li>
				<li><strong>Campaign Management:</strong> AI-driven marketing campaign tools</li>
				<li><strong>Market Intelligence:</strong> AI competitive analysis and market research</li>
			</ul>
			
			<h2>How We Select Tools</h2>
			<p>
				Each tool in our directory is evaluated based on:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Effectiveness and performance</li>
				<li>User experience and ease of use</li>
				<li>Integration capabilities</li>
				<li>Value for money</li>
				<li>Customer support and resources</li>
				<li>Innovation and unique features</li>
			</ul>
			
			<h2>Stay Updated</h2>
			<p>
				The AI marketing landscape evolves rapidly. We regularly update our directory with new tools 
				and fresh information to ensure you always have access to the latest and greatest AI marketing solutions.
			</p>
			
			<h2>Contact Us</h2>
			<p>
				Have a suggestion for a tool we should include? Want to provide feedback? 
				Feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:contact@aimarketingtools.com">contact@aimarketingtools.com</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		position: relative;
	}

	.hero-content {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		position: relative;
		padding: 2rem 0;
	}
	
	.hero-glow {
		position: absolute;
		top: 50%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
		width: 80%;
		height: 70%;
		background: radial-gradient(
			ellipse at center,
			rgba(80, 200, 255, 0.15) 0%,
			rgba(180, 100, 255, 0.1) 40%,
			transparent 70%
		);
		filter: blur(40px);
		z-index: -1;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.about h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(80, 200, 255), rgb(180, 100, 255));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(80, 200, 255, 0.3);
		position: relative;
		display: inline-block;
	}
	
	.about h1::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: -10px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 80px;
		height: 3px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(80, 200, 255), rgb(180, 100, 255));
		border-radius: 3px;
	}

	.content {
		background-color: rgba(25, 28, 45, 0.7);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		border: 1px solid rgba(80, 200, 255, 0.1);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	
	.content::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background: linear-gradient(
			135deg,
			rgba(80, 200, 255, 0.05) 0%,
			transparent 50%,
			rgba(180, 100, 255, 0.05) 100%
		);
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	h2 {
		color: rgb(80, 200, 255);
		margin: 1.8rem 0 1rem;
		font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	p {
		color: rgba(180, 190, 220, 0.9);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	ul {
		margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
		color: rgba(180, 190, 220, 0.9);
	}

	li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		position: relative;
	}
	
	li::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: -1rem;
		top: 0.6rem;
		width: 6px;
		height: 6px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(80, 200, 255), rgb(180, 100, 255));
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	a {
		color: rgb(80, 200, 255);
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		position: relative;
	}

	a::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: -2px;
		left: 0;
		width: 0;
		height: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(80, 200, 255), rgb(180, 100, 255));
		transition: width 0.3s ease;
	}

	a:hover {
		color: rgb(180, 100, 255);
	}

	a:hover::after {
		width: 100%;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.content {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
